query:
DELETE FROM tokens
                WHERE
                    l2_address IN (
                        SELECT
                            SUBSTRING(key, 12, 20)
                        FROM
                            storage_logs
                        WHERE
                            storage_logs.address = $1
                            AND miniblock_number > $2
                            AND NOT EXISTS (
                                SELECT
                                    1
                                FROM
                                    storage_logs AS s
                                WHERE
                                    s.hashed_key = storage_logs.hashed_key
                                    AND (s.miniblock_number, s.operation_number) >= (storage_logs.miniblock_number, storage_logs.operation_number)
                                    AND s.value = $3
                            )
                    )
